          <p>My favored &#8220;eating plan&#8221; (let&#8217;s not say &#8220;diet&#8221;) is the No S Diet: no snacks, seconds, sweets, or sugar except on days beginning with &#8220;S.&#8221; Reinhard runs a good forum were people who like the idea support each other. You also might enjoy reading his &#8220;manifesto&#8221; on how he created it.</p>
<p>I like it because it doesn&#8217;t require me to buy special foods, it&#8217;s easy to remember wherever I am (home, cafeteria) and I don&#8217;t need to carry one of those calorie counter books with me.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.nosdiet.com" rel="nofollow">http://www.nosdiet.com</a></p>
